reviews.review_text: The cleanest McDonald s I ve been to. The staff all smile and treat you like a human being. The manager to the front staff very kind. I had an issue ordering on the app today and they replaced my items for me easily without problem. I apologized and they made it easy for me. Simran made me feel at ease about it. They re lucky to have her as an employee, but also human decency is hard to come by these days.
Newly renovated look makes the place more open and has more seating. Clean and tidy areas conducive for dining in.

I have been going to Tim Hortons down the street and had a bad experience so decided to try this Mcdonalds. I dont often feel compelled to leave reviews, but the staff was so friendly (literally greeting customers by name), were accommodating to my very modified order and even repeated back to avoid mistakes and saved me a trip to the bank by selling me a ton of change I needed for laundry. Coffee was also surprisingly better than the Tim Hortons.
Sausage and egg mc muffins  low calories

Its a tidy place and the service is quick and incredibly friendly! I love to stop  by here before or after work for a small energizer. All the food Ive been served here has all been freshly made and not stale or cold at all!
Dropped in for a quick bite and found the place very clean and quiet. My quarter pounder was perfect and the fries were good.
Amazing customer service and managers, especially on the night shift, my favorite location by far.
Good deal going on for $1. Need it to break the heat anytime.

Interesting but hardly surprising...you will never see a regular hamburger or a regular cheeseburger pictured or listed on the big screens behind the counter. You only see far more expensive options. Just know, these far cheaper options are always, albeit reluctantly available!

Honestly I Just come here For a coffee mostly Or I hop across the road to leons i go back and forth.  This mcdonalds is very Quick and very Efficient. Workers you can tell work Very Hard. I give 5 stars For Them.

I was quite pleasantly surprised by the amazing service, even when going through the drive-thru. I had asked for unsalted fries and they made very fresh and piping hot. Ketchup was included without being asked and service was provided with a smile. Id visit here again whenever Im in the neighborhood.

We had an issue last week and spoke to manager Nav. She promised to replace our entire order on our next visit. She was working when we returned today and personally packed and processed our order to perfection. Thank you Nav and the team at McDonald s!

I have been coming here a lot lately drive through and walking in and I have to say, every time the staff is so friendly! Honestly for people working at McDonald s I can t believe how cheerfully they treat me. When I come into a fast food establishment i have zero expectations, because it s fast food after all but I have had no issues with any of my orders in a long time! Orders are correct and quick every time. And I come all timesof the day, morning, afternoon, evening and late nights! Treat your servers with respect y all!
Manager and staff were very kind and accommodating, so appreciative!

This specific location has really got their act together. During these Covid 19 times this MC McDonalds has gone from a barely  acceptable experience to one of the most consistent and satisfying. When i order through a delivery service my order has not been incorrect once. It is always hot and fresh, made and delivered promptly. I am seriously impressed by how much this restaurant has stepped up its game lately. Thank you for doing so much better.
This restaurant has gotten quite the glow-up over the years. Its always been a great place to stop at for lunch when I lived close to White Rock Beach some years back.

Its really good to download their app as so many offers available and u get to choose easily. The burgers are yumm but don t expect the size of burger as of whopper (actually I expected  ), overall 5 stars for the taste n service.

Much greater food and staff than other McDonalds near them. They have a great location, near the library, movie theater and more. They have a playground, which is great for kids. They have much more high quality beef and chicken than most McDonalds. They have self-pay kiosks and a drive-through which some McDonalds dont have. They have a lot of staff, and more than enough to handle the customers.

I just went through the drive-thru with my friend and I have got to say   Deepali is the nicest McDonalds worker I have ever had dealt with. We both have had a very long day and her kindness brightened our whole night. No one else was in the line so she took the time to chat and ask us how our days were. Definitely will be coming back to this location.
Easy convenient drive-through service

Quick service, its been kept impeccably clean through Covid, when theyve had dine in available its been well spaced out with every other table taped off, meals (especially fries) are always fresh, and online orders are always ready upon arrival.

Love the coffee and danishes, especially the blue berry cream cheese one. Service at McDonalds is always amazing and readily do they get your order wrong. (Note to self: comment on the one Tim Hortons which have literally always messed my order.). So McDonalds has the best coffee bean and are consistently good and consistent.

They have handled customers in a very professional and efficient way during this pandemic. They are really making a huge effort to keep the place absolutely clean and sterilized and the service is very fast and friendly.

Long waits when there are lots of orders. Doesnt have ice cream when the machine is broken. Crew do their job and are in fact human, so some mistakes are made. Exactly what should be expected. Stop complaining about McDicks

Best Mcdonalds this side of the river. The manager is a great guy, went out of his way to bring my friend bottled water when we were stuck in White Rock at 1:00AM on the morning after Canada day. Saved our night for sure! Its worth going down here for food as it is better quality than some other Mcdonalds locations! The Mcdoubles are high quality.
They remodelled this place really well. Good hard working staff do their best and the food is always fresh.
Tried the new chicken sandwich with ghost peppers. It was great and spicy. Store was clean and well organized.
My go to place for a cup of hot coffee and one of their splendid muffins. Clean place with staff that cares for every customer.
Was pretty satisfied with my visit there and fast good service
Restaurant outside maybe on the older side but the inside looks great. Fast service and great quality burgers and fries.
Night staff very friendly, always a warm welcome when ordering my late night McDs. Friendly faces always ask how your night is going. NUMBER 1 MC Ds!
Very good very responsive and most important very fast thanks guys for your fresh warm fast services food!! I suggest everyone to stop by for a quick good meal!!
Very practical for a busy day.  Fast food with many locations and Mc Donalds always offers delicious meals.
Great service they now offer to bring your food to your table then are asking you if there is anything else they can help with. Very clean and fast
Crystal was very nice and positive from the beginning to the end. She complimented my daughters hoodie and made our visit to McDonalds very enjoyable.
Helpful, , knowledgeable staff Great place to shop Nice selection of electric guitars
I always come here for a nice, traditional vanilla cone. Perfect for a sunny day at White Rock.
New renovation is super nice. Really sketchy before, but it s way better. Hopefully it stays nice
All in all, hittin Don s on the way back from a rough night of D&D is always a great time. I will mention however, it took a while for my order to be received.
Good prompt drive thru service. Food was hot and quick. The girl at the window was way too friendly  lol.
I like this location of McDonalds. Easy to get in and out Im close to many main arteries.
Staff are super helpful and restaraunt is cleaned to a superb degree! A wonderful choice for those in the White Rock/South Surrey area!
They have really good staff and proper seating for dine-in and for the delivery guys they have proper place to wait.
Very friendly and quick service from the drive thru staff
Excellent service on the drive thru thanks.
Got a burger, drink and fries for close to $10. Good deal and good food.... Nuff Said (c)
They made the best chicken nuggets!!! Great customer service. I love McDonald s.
Love the unlimited salad, generous portions and courteous service. Well worth the wait.
Nice and quick service late in the evening, staff are really chill yet professional, very kind.
We re really fast! Stopped in while waiting for the bus and still made the bus in time!
I really like mcdonalds even though I shouldnt eat here so much
I love the Happy Meal toys and food plus the drinks . Also I love the Big Mac Mal too
Very fast service, absolutely delicious food and great customer service!
Im loving everything about this location efficient staff, food nice fast and easy
Restaurant was clean and efficiently run. Serve was quick and food was warm and tasty.
McDonalds Restaurant  on 152 nd  st ,  South  Surrey  is  Fast  &  Takes  your  Meal. TO the  Table.
its really good One of my favourite place in the whole canada I love Macdonalds
The app, the coffee, the service. McDonalds is great for fast food so you can get back to work.
The counter servers are very nice and polite, along with fast and efficient at this particular location
This one is much better than the South Surrey location. Go here if you have the choice between the two.
Great service great place to enjoy a meal or a cup of coffee.
hot coffee, friendly staff, great decor,
Nice food and staff. Super busy area
Fast sevice, nice taste, kind people in my opinion
Great except for groups of men that sound like kackling hens
Very friendly and fast drive thru staff!
Recently renovated as of summer 2022.
Excellent customer service. Fast and friendly.
Not the friendliest staff, but its usually pretty busy though
Great food, great price n great service
Good hot fast food. And free smiles
Convenient location in White Rock from Semiahmoo Mall, Bank, the Library and Dollarama.
Good breakfast
Nice cheese burger and Mc flurry Oreo...
Great atmosphere
Always standard fare. Good when u are hungry.
Good hard working staff, never failed to impress.
It was awesome McLovin it
I didnt get stabbed today
Clean washrooms. Good service with social distancing
I wanted no ice they gave me no ice.  5/5

How can you not love their McNuggets?
Its a McDonalds. If you like McDonalds, youll appreciate this one.

Kids play structure! So hard to find these days.
